        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">The values for COD, BOD, TOC, and DOC used in this inventory are calculated from the amount of organic substancesl in the treated waste water assuming a carbon conversion of 96% for COD. For the calculation of the values for BOD and DOC the worst case scenario BOD = COD and TOC = DOC is used.</comment>
